commit_message: Add OCHROdb, a database of open chromatin regions, https://dhs.ccm.sickkids.ca/
Update TOBIAS ATAC-seq TFBS analysis, https://github.com/loosolab/TOBIAS
Move databases section on top, reorganize
Add ATAC-seq analysis considerations, Reske et al. 2020
Add maxATAC into new Deep Learning section
Move Chromap, SNAP into RNA-seq Alignment section
Add enhancers, normalization sections, LILI, CHIPIN
Start broad peak analysis section, add epic2
Add CUT&RUN methods from Vinjamur et al. 2020
Add UCSC unusual regions on assembly structure
Add Awesome ATAC-seq analysis by Nathan Sheffield
Add marge - API for HOMER in R
Add LISA, epigenetic Landscape In silico Subtraction analysis
Add HMCan and HMCan-diff histone peak callers
Add DNAse-seq section and Liu 2018 tools review
Add Dimensionality Reduction for scATAC-seq Data
Add RSEG - ChIP-seq broad domain analysis
Add ROSE, RANK ORDERING OF SUPER-ENHANCERS
Add Genrich - Detecting sites of genomic enrichment in ChIP-seq and ATAC-seq
Add Toolkit for Cistrome Data Browser
Add Zerone: a ChIP-seq discretizer for multiple replicates with built-in quality control
